body: "Audit GitHub issues, PRs, checks, dependency/security reports, full history, package contents, and real multi-repo behavior. Preserve unrelated work. Generate CHANGELOG.md and release notes with pm-changelog. Verify daily change-gated GitHub/npm/Bun release automation. Run Greptile before push, then bot review loops to green."
